              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3572544088407223519">This book is full of sorrow &amp; truth. The sorrow of real life &amp; of the Catholic church &amp; of human frailty. I am a pagan born &amp; raised, I went into the Catholic Church &amp; found power misused &amp; ashes. I am sadder &amp; wiser for this knowledge, yet still in the church because of the beauty &amp; glory I do find there.</span>

          </span>
